{
  "stem": "628.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When you come back from school, you play in the streets with your neighbors, which are not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And life went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Child only sees the happiness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they-- so, you know, I came to about 10 years of age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One of my sisters, Lotti, she got tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] very ill, she became very ill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My mother came, because she lived somewhere else, but she came and wanted to take her to a sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the Germans wouldn't allow it at moment, already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Being a Jewish girl, there was no saving to be done already at that time, and they couldn't cure her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So that-- Lotti died at the age of 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berlin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was already the biggest loss for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can remember my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had-- the week before she died, she was lying in her bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She probably weighed 30 kilos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandmother slept with her the last week of her life to be near her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When the day happened that she died, what happened on at our house is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they put her into the-- they cleaned her up, how it's done properly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was put into the little box there for a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she looked like a beautiful girl, a young Yiddish girl, I saw so beautiful, being that already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, when that happened, I was in the Jewish school, in Munchener Strasse, where the synagogue was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was also where we could play after the school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they called me, Lotti is dying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And must have been 15 minutes away or something-- I was running like mad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was standing next to the bed-- my grandfather, my grandmother, and Gisella.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
